.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1726%2c20211130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,簡,1726,20211130,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1726","JDATE":"20211130","JTITLE":"竊盜"}